= Flash Content

Flash Content is a simple Radiant extension to help reference Adobe flash files within Radiant's pages, snippets and layouts.

= Download and Install

To install flash content, jun run

  cd <RADIANT ROOT>
  git clone git://github.com/ceaser/radiant-flash_content-extension.git vendor/extensions/flash_content
  rake production radiant:extensions:flash_content:update

= Using

There are two new tags included with the flash content extension. 

Required to add a reference to the swfobject script
<r:flash_content:include />

Writes the code necessary to reference and start a flash animation
<r:flash_content:link />

Detail documenation and usage examples are available inside the page admin under the "Available Tags" links